Mark 11-11 <pb/><f>ⓞ</f> And he entered Jerusalem and went into the temple. And when he had looked around at everything, as it was already late, <f>ⓟ</f>he went out to Bethany with the twelve.
Mark 11-12 <pb/><f>ⓠ</f> On the following day, when they came from Bethany, <f>ⓡ</f>he was hungry.
