Mark 11-27 <pb/><f>ⓠ</f> And they came again to Jerusalem. And as he was walking in the temple, the chief priests and the scribes and the elders came to him,
Mark 11-28 and they said to him, <f>ⓡ</f>“By what authority are you doing these things, or who gave you this authority to do them?”
